  <section id="projects" class="section">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <ul class="project-list">
      <li>
        <strong>KVCache Storage</strong>
        <p>Unified DRAM/SSD KVCache management as an independent daemon, decoupled from inference frameworks (vLLM/sglang/internal), reporting KVCache metadata for scheduler-aware scheduling.<a href="/kvcache-en/">[Details]</a></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>KVCache Simulator</strong>
        <p>Estimates KVCache capacity requirements and evaluates cache-aware scheduling algorithms, saving GPU time and engineering resources.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Kata-Runtime Offloading on DPU</strong>
        <p>Offloaded QEMU Kata Container and emulated devices to DPU, optimized for high-density deployment and concurrent startup, achieving 1x density improvement.<a href="/dpu-kata-en/">[Details]</a></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Titanium: Lightweight ARM TrustZone VMM</strong>
        <p>Leveraged ARMv8.4 SEL2 to build a lightweight VMM in TrustZone, in collaboration with HiSilicon. Available in C and Rust.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Public Cloud IOMMU Performance Optimization</strong>
        <p>Optimized NUMA-unbalanced IOMMU PageTable allocation in SRIOV + VFIO setups.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

